title: #92Noon!  10am Hour 7/21 - John Bonnes/News to the Maxx
description: John Bonnes hangs out in-studio to talk about Byron Buxton's season so far, Kenta Maeda's potential return, & much more.  Plus, Maxx Fuller provides today's sports news including: a potential Jimmy G trade & Kirby Smart's new contract.
